Class LongHashMap<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.badlogic.gdx.utils.LongHashMap<T>

public class LongHashMap<T>
extends java.lang.Object

An unordered map that uses long keys. Avoids the boxing that occurs with HashMap.

Author:
Nathan Sweet , christop widulle
